The CARTAvis scripted client. To install, perform the following steps:

- from the scriptedClient directory, run python setup.py sdist
- cd dist
- run tar -xvf on the tarball in the dist directory
- change to the resulting directory
- run sudo python setup.py install

cartavis should now be installed on your system, enabling it to be
imported from anywhere. To test, run the following in a Python session:

    import carta.cartavis
